title: Pile oscillator measurements of the absorption cross sections for slow neutrons

x4freetext: Pile oscillator measurements of the absorption cross
ratio data is for pile spectrum, Maxwellian thermal a
average cross sections, while the normalised values
are corrected to mono-energetic 2200 m/sec values.
